* '''Player:''' Brentle you say? So you knew him then?
* '''Bartender:''' Yeah, this belongs to 'Brentle Vahn', he's quite a common customer, though I've not seen him in a while.
* '''Bartender:''' He was talking to some shifty looking wizard the other day. I don't know his name, but I'd recognise him if I saw him.
